            "type": "text",
            "text": "Advanced Options for LLM Chat Applications"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Beyond temperature, LLM applications expose a second tier of parameters — system prompts, stop sequences, max tokens, model selection, and context window management — that power users rely on but new users do not need immediately. This section covers the implementation of each control, their validation rules, and how they wire to the Anthropic API."
          }
        ]
      },
